Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.20,0:00:10.30,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,我的女儿
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.30,0:00:13.97,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,日后会成为给主上殿下\N呈上白瓷碗的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.97,0:00:15.81,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,什么 既然有了孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.81,0:00:19.11,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,您先答应我保护好这孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.11,0:00:21.68,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,我的子女 只有一个毓道已经够了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.68,0:00:22.78,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,井儿
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.78,0:00:24.99,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你要向我爹道歉 马上
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.99,0:00:26.82,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你居然还有女儿
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.82,0:00:30.12,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,殿下登基不知不觉二十年了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.12,0:00:33.06,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,趁此机会我要推荐世子册封
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.06,0:00:35.26,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,这回要处决的对象 是光海
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.26,0:00:37.46,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,江天已经开始活动了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.46,0:00:39.30,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,做一个宗庙祭的祭器
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.30,0:00:41.87,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,我会奉御令制作祭器
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.87,0:00:43.70,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,知道他是何人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.70,0:00:47.74,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,是在恭嫔的茶杯里下毒的人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.74,0:00:48.84,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,居然给母亲下毒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.84,0:00:53.25,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,这是太祖大王盛著建国气韵制作的\N珍贵的坛子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.25,0:00:55.08,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你要如性命般珍惜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.75,0:01:00.22,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,不可以啊 王兄
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.52,0:01:04.26,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,王兄
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.67,0:01:22.24,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你 你怎么没有接住啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.44,0:01:25.55,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.91,0:01:28.85,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,为何看我 是你没接住啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.85,0:01:31.42,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你为何连这个都抓不好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.42,0:01:32.52,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,王兄
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.52,0:01:36.92,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,难 难道你这是在怪我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.70,0:01:43.90,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,不是说不是就成为不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.00,0:01:47.93,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,是 是我的错
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.93,0:01:51.97,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,醉酒后都不会走道的王兄\N让你进宗庙祭
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.97,0:01:53.07,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,就是我的错
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.21,0:01:59.68,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你 你要如何
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.55,0:02:07.39,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,珲儿 珲儿
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.75,0:02:09.22,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,珲儿等等
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.32,0:02:14.36,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,珲儿 珲儿 你这是怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.36,0:02:18.40,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,都说了是我的错 因此也要由我负责
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.40,0:02:22.44,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你这是疯了吗 你真的要向父王禀报吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.31,0:02:30.14,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,珲儿 珲儿等等
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.51,0:02:32.71,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,珲儿 珲儿等等啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.55,0:02:37.12,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,这就不对了 你要想清楚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.12,0:02:40.42,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,想得越多 越会害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.42,0:02:44.09,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,因此对王兄的埋怨也会越大\N我不想那样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.29,0:02:48.86,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你这是真打算要使我难堪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.96,0:02:50.70,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,王兄
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.70,0:02:54.00,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,是父王如性命般珍惜的坛子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.00,0:02:57.67,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,父王肯定会重罚的 你怎能如实禀报呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.04,0:03:00.97,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,再加上 我还没有醒酒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.97,0:03:02.81,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,以这副样子怎能拜见父王
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.81,0:03:07.58,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,如此怕父王的人\N怎能让事情发生到这个地步呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.32,0:03:10.88,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,-当初你就\N-闭嘴 我不需要你来教训
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.35,0:03:16.39,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,父王如性命般珍惜的\N你为何放在那上面呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.86,0:03:21.53,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你以为你能平安无事吗\N好 那我们就走著瞧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.08,0:03:43.92,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,仁嫔在里面
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.92,0:03:48.32,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,是吗 那我们下次再来吧 珲儿
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.32,0:03:49.42,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,进来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.71,0:04:12.18,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你们来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.28,0:04:18.05,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你们来了吗 父王 既然王兄们来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.05,0:04:20.25,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,那么小儿就退下了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.25,0:04:23.19,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,好 辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.16,0:04:31.26,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,有何事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.00,0:04:35.30,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,我有重要事相告
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.07,0:04:41.17,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.52,0:04:53.65,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,还在磨蹭什么 有话快说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.32,0:05:00.99,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,看来臣妾还是先退下吧 殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.83,0:05:05.03,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,到底有什么话要说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.03,0:05:07.97,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,真的是在嫔面前不能说吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.70,0:05:14.57,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,不是的 我说 今日祭阳所
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.59,0:05:29.99,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,来了乙檀制作的祭器
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.93,0:05:33.66,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,於是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.13,0:05:39.53,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,能否用在宗庙祭 我想由父王过目
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.27,0:05:42.10,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你这不争气的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.10,0:05:44.30,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,寡人不是封你为副提调吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.30,0:05:47.97,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,决定也要你出 责任也要由你担
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.97,0:05:49.81,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,为何要烦寡人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.18,0:05:51.28,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,很惭愧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.38,0:05:55.32,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你呢 你来做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.32,0:05:57.88,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,什 么都不是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.45,0:06:01.92,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你喝酒了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.66,0:06:04.86,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,没 没有 就寝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.59,0:06:07.06,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,走 走吧 珲儿
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.87,0:06:18.07,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,做得很好 编得还不错
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.44,0:06:21.01,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,差点做了信城的好事了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.01,0:06:22.84,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,这不是好事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.68,0:06:27.25,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,如今连向父王如实相告的机会\N也错失掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.98,0:06:29.45,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,该如何是好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.45,0:06:33.49,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,是啊 你应该感到害怕\N闯了这么大的祸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.49,0:06:34.96,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,我还真是担心你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.42,0:06:38.26,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,所有的错都应该由你来承担
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.26,0:06:41.56,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,可身为兄长 我岂能旁观弟弟的危险呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.93,0:06:44.87,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,-我也会帮你想想办法\N-不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.60,0:06:47.43,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,既然说所有都是我的责任
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.43,0:06:50.37,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,办法也由我一个人想
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.51,0:07:00.65,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,好久不见 你怕责怪才没有来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.48,0:07:04.68,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,我很惭愧 娘娘
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.68,0:07:08.72,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,我不会再因为册封世子之事来责备你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.09,0:07:13.49,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,殿下哪是那么轻易决定的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.49,0:07:14.96,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,娘娘
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.33,0:07:17.16,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,现在才正式开始
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.00,0:07:23.77,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,昨晚光海君和临海君拜见殿下了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.50,0:07:27.81,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,一定是祭阳所出了问题
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.18,0:07:31.48,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你快去查看 到底是出了什么问题
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.21,0:07:34.41,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你到底是做什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.41,0:07:35.52,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,有何事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.88,0:07:39.55,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,昨晚祭阳所似乎出事了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.02,0:07:42.49,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,这种话 我不是在你口中
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.49,0:07:45.43,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,而是要在仁嫔娘娘那里听到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.43,0:07:47.26,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你让我的脸面往哪搁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.99,0:07:48.73,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,很惭愧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.73,0:07:54.60,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,就想著毫无意义的乙檀\N眼耳都被蒙住了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.60,0:07:58.27,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,到底祭阳所发生何事 你快去查清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.22,0:08:15.52,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,那个不是乙檀的祭器吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.36,0:08:18.46,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,先出去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.82,0:08:53.69,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,看来是有名良班家令郎\N到底有何事来找我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.77,0:09:04.34,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,打碎的茶杯 修复成原有模样的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.44,0:09:07.27,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,知道这种人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.27,0:09:10.58,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,这种事就要去找分院的陶瓷匠啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.58,0:09:14.61,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,就因为不能去找分院 才回来这的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.61,0:09:18.29,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,听说这里贩卖明瓷器非常活跃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.29,0:09:21.59,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,明那边 没有人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.59,0:09:26.36,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,这里只交易的物品 不会交易人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.36,0:09:30.03,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,报酬会充分支付给你的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.03,0:09:31.87,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,还是请回吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.90,0:09:37.74,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,大人 大人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.67,0:09:44.34,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,我叫火灵 日前在酒家见过一面
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.55,0:09:49.48,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,您在找修补碎碗的人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.58,0:09:52.42,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,去找井儿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.79,0:09:53.89,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,井儿
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.89,0:10:00.13,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,是 一有空就会修补碎碗\N有时连师父都认不出呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.13,0:10:01.60,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,她是谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.60,0:10:03.80,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,乙坦还有女儿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.16,0:10:10.77,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,不是和泰道哥一起在山上见到的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.87,0:10:15.54,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你是说\N那个叫井儿的孩子那天也在山上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.01,0:10:20.68,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,我去见一下破器匠 你要守好家
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.78,0:10:25.09,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,破器匠大人的话 是不是火灵的爹
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.09,0:10:27.29,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,那就是说能带回火灵了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.65,0:10:29.49,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,那也要看她的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.22,0:10:32.06,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,谁知道她愿不愿回来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.43,0:10:33.53,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,不会啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.89,0:10:36.83,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,火灵肯定也想快点见到我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.83,0:10:38.67,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,一定要带回来 一定哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.13,0:10:41.97,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,要好好守好家
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.34,0:10:46.01,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,可不要像上次似的 玩得连手都弄破了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.11,0:10:50.41,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,放心吧 我不会离开家门一步
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.14,0:10:51.88,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,我去去就回
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.51,0:11:22.71,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,哥 哥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.44,0:11:25.65,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你怎么出来了 禁足令解开了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.85,0:11:29.32,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,是不是偷跑出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.32,0:11:31.52,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,我爹去火灵家了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.72,0:11:36.29,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,对了 你教我骑马吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.02,0:11:39.23,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,小心点骑 别害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.43,0:11:44.00,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,马儿 要多关照哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.81,0:11:53.91,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,握紧缰绳
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.91,0:11:54.64,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,赤兔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.58,0:11:59.41,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,-井儿\N-快救我 哥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.98,0:12:02.72,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,井儿
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.82,0:12:06.02,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,哥 危险
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.07,0:12:22.17,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,大人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.31,0:12:28.78,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,井儿 没事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.45,0:12:33.55,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,井儿
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.28,0:12:35.38,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,先看看大人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.12,0:12:37.22,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,您还好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.25,0:12:43.46,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,每次见面都这么惊天动地
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.93,0:12:46.76,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,大人 那是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.10,0:12:58.51,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,大人 怎么是好啊 都摔坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.48,0:13:07.68,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,难道就没有 赎回火灵的办法了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.05,0:13:09.88,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你到底欠了多少钱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.35,0:13:13.19,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,这件事你就别再提了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.92,0:13:15.02,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,难受啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.06,0:13:20.53,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,以后就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.26,0:13:22.36,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.73,0:13:24.20,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,我俩之间 何必呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.93,0:13:28.24,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,殿下不是很爱惜 你的手艺的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.24,0:13:29.34,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,谁知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.34,0:13:32.27,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,指不定哪一天 你就成了朗厅了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.64,0:13:34.11,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,说什么胡话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.47,0:13:37.78,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,别说这些没用的\N还是想办法赎回火灵吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.75,0:13:48.79,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,跪著干什么\N我都说了我是在等乙檀回来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.79,0:13:51.73,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,大人 我爹是无辜的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.09,0:13:56.50,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,要杀就杀我 要贬为奴我也一力承担
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.86,0:13:57.96,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,求您放过我爹
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.96,0:13:59.07,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,不是的 大人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.07,0:14:01.27,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,那天在山上是我要井儿逃走的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.27,0:14:02.74,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,要罚就罚我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.74,0:14:05.67,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.67,0:14:07.51,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,乙坦到底什么时候回来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.34,0:14:10.81,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,您太过分了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.55,0:14:14.48,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,小女都说了 甘愿领受处罚了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.48,0:14:17.78,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,您为什么死咬著我爹不放
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.89,0:14:20.72,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,我什么时候说过怎么著你爹了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.92,0:14:27.33,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,那好 只要我处罚你就可以了是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.06,0:14:31.37,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,是 谢谢您 谢谢您 大人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.87,0:14:40.17,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,什么处罚都愿意
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.17,0:14:45.68,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,是 大人 那是自然 小女之罪岂是等闲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.41,0:14:48.62,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,竟敢拧大人您的胳膊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.45,0:14:52.65,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,还说谎要看到您的胳膊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.65,0:14:54.12,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,必须斩下您的胳膊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.86,0:14:57.06,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,不相信您是王子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.06,0:14:59.99,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,王子 真是可笑
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.99,0:15:01.09,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,混帐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.09,0:15:03.30,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,还对您说出大不敬的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.77,0:15:05.87,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,何止
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.23,0:15:08.44,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,还为了就颤栗的您
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.80,0:15:12.47,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,竟然把自己的裙子 盖住了您的玉体
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.47,0:15:13.94,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,别动
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.35,0:15:21.65,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,身体一暖 就不那么难受了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.65,0:15:22.38,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,打住
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.12,0:15:26.42,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,喂 那个... 快住口
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.62,0:15:31.19,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,我本人知道的很清楚 不用再用你说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.56,0:15:33.03,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,好的 大人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.96,0:15:37.80,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,我要处罚与你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.90,0:15:40.37,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,快闭上眼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.96,0:16:07.53,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,还剩下两下 快闭上眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.53,0:16:10.10,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,这就是处罚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.10,0:16:11.20,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,不愿意
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.20,0:16:13.03,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,哪里 怎么会不愿意
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.40,0:16:14.50,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,请快行刑
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.62,0:16:38.73,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,走了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.56,0:16:41.29,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,走
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.03,0:16:43.13,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.23,0:16:46.80,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,这就完事了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.63,0:16:50.47,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,不如找井儿看看
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.20,0:16:56.71,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,算了吧 那种黄毛丫头能知道什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.71,0:17:00.38,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,大人 稍等片刻
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.48,0:17:04.05,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,大人稍等片刻
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.15,0:17:06.25,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你怎么追过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.62,0:17:09.56,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,大人 小女孩是放不下心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.56,0:17:12.49,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,非得挨那两下弹指是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.86,0:17:18.00,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,不是那件事 我给您修复那件碎瓷器
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.10,0:17:19.83,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.83,0:17:22.77,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,既然是我打碎的 就交给我来修复吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.50,0:17:25.71,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,俗话说有其父必有其女
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.17,0:17:28.64,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你知道这是什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.38,0:17:31.95,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,必定是贵重瓷器 这当然能猜到了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.05,0:17:35.25,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,这可不是你这黄毛丫头可以修复的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.98,0:17:39.29,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,大人 我虽然看起来有点毛毛躁躁
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.29,0:17:41.86,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,可是修复瓷器却很有两下子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.86,0:17:42.96,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.96,0:17:44.06,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,都说不可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.79,0:17:47.73,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,修复了这个 你就成了犯了谋逆大罪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.73,0:17:51.03,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,大人 不相信我您就直说了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.03,0:17:55.80,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,不就是修复瓷器吗\N有什么大不了的 说什么谋逆大罪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.80,0:17:59.11,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,难道还能大过 对您犯的大不敬之罪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.84,0:18:01.31,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,快交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.14,0:18:04.61,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,喂 喂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.28,0:18:10.12,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,需要几天之内完成
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.85,0:18:13.42,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,真的 有信心吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.79,0:18:16.36,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,到时候您可不要被吓到了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.66,0:18:21.86,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,五天 给你五天时间
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.33,0:18:26.27,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,足够了 路上小心 大人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.28,0:18:38.75,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,我叫你们好好看著
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.15,0:18:45.35,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,竟然不知道他去了哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.35,0:18:48.66,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,您不是说只要不让他\N去找殿下就可以了吗 大人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.66,0:18:50.86,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,既然出了宫 您就可以放心了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.86,0:18:52.33,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你小子 还敢顶嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.06,0:18:56.36,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,怎么不叫醒我 或者跟踪他
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.73,0:18:58.20,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你 你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.20,0:19:00.40,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,立刻去打探他都干了些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.40,0:19:01.50,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.27,0:19:09.21,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,怎么还杵在这里不动\N还不去康宁店守著
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.58,0:19:12.15,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,要是光海出现\N你一定要给我阻止他见殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.88,0:19:13.98,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,是 大人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.65,0:19:18.75,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,竟然出了宫
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.14,0:19:43.34,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.08,0:19:48.48,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,您此行是不是为了 太祖大王坛之事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.48,0:19:53.99,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,光海来过这里 他怎么说\N说是我打碎的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.99,0:19:56.56,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,大人 莫非是您打碎的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.39,0:20:00.59,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,不是我 是光海
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.70,0:20:05.00,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,真的是光海君大人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.00,0:20:08.30,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,混帐 现在重要的不是这事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.30,0:20:11.24,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,要寻根溯源的话 也只能怪教唆我的你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.24,0:20:13.44,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你就是罪魁祸首
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.44,0:20:17.11,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,说起我的本意\N倒更希望打碎祭器的人是乙坦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.11,0:20:18.21,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,给我粘上
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.31,0:20:20.41,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.52,0:20:24.08,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,此事都怪你 所以由你...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.08,0:20:24.82,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.55,0:20:29.59,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,由朗厅你来修复不是应该的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.32,0:20:31.06,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,大人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.43,0:20:35.46,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,办不到 你也配做朝鲜第一沙器匠吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.46,0:20:38.40,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,大人 太祖大人坛是何等贵重之物啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.40,0:20:41.70,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,打碎是谋逆大罪 修复也是谋逆大罪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.44,0:20:45.01,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,微臣实在不明白\N您为什么非要让微臣成为谋逆之臣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.94,0:20:49.04,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,大人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.41,0:20:51.61,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,这是机会啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.61,0:20:52.35,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,什么机会
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.35,0:20:54.92,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,碎瓷现在在谁手里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.92,0:20:57.48,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,当然是在光海手里了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.48,0:21:01.15,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,可光海君大人没来分院
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.52,0:21:05.19,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,那 他还会去找谁
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.39,0:21:08.13,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,对上了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.86,0:21:10.33,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,这次是 这个
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.06,0:21:11.80,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,对上了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.27,0:21:14.37,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.20,0:21:17.30,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,乙檀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.67,0:21:18.77,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,是的 大人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.51,0:21:20.97,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,是乙檀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.71,0:21:26.11,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,光海去找乙檀 怎么就成了机会
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.11,0:21:30.15,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,宗庙祭时文武百官都会出席
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.15,0:21:37.12,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,如果到时指认打碎者是光海君大人\N修复者是乙檀的话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.12,0:21:38.96,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,不可 万万不可
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.96,0:21:40.43,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,要是光海他...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.43,0:21:45.57,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,一举除掉光海君和乙坦的绝好机会
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.03,0:21:48.87,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,您想要任之溜走
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.97,0:21:52.54,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,光海可是我弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.37,0:21:59.15,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,也是争夺世子之位的 劲敌
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.85,0:22:10.16,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,我要做怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.36,0:22:17.13,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,相信我 等著看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.70,0:22:49.43,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.16,0:22:50.90,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.47,0:22:54.57,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,不是这个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.40,0:22:58.24,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,这是陶土块呀
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.07,0:23:04.48,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,怎么没有呢  应该是在这里呀
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.85,0:23:07.78,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,没有那一块就做不出来呀
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.78,0:23:10.72,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,所以说为什么要揽下那个活儿呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.45,0:23:13.65,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,哥哥 叫你回家
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.65,0:23:15.49,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你怎么不回家 还要在这里唠叨呀
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.43,0:23:20.63,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你这个性格真是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.10,0:23:25.77,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,如果是柳乙檀的事情 就不要再说了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.50,0:23:30.17,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,我是作为边首 来找郎厅大人的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.74,0:23:36.04,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,祭阳所出了问题
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.51,0:23:40.45,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,有个碗消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.81,0:23:43.38,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,太祖大王的碗是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.38,0:23:46.32,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,那个不是消失了 而是弄碎了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.32,0:23:48.89,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,您是怎么知道的呀
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.89,0:23:50.36,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你是怎么知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.70,0:24:01.37,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,要给副提调光海君大人\N报告这件事情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.37,0:24:06.87,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,打碎这个的人 正是光海君大人
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.28,0:24:13.85,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,那光海君大人 会怎么样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.85,0:24:15.68,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,会出大事的 不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.68,0:24:20.45,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,所以大人肯定会想著要复原那个的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.76,0:24:24.86,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.86,0:24:25.59,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,给你的话
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.59,0:24:27.43,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,那我就去找光海君大人
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.43,0:24:29.26,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,我帮他复原
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.26,0:24:34.40,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,那就会变成大逆罪人 难道你不知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.14,0:24:40.27,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,知道 可不能看著大人成为大逆罪人呀
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.31,0:24:46.88,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你觉得他会找你帮忙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.88,0:24:50.92,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,应该已经找别人了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.92,0:24:54.22,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,没有这一块 就无法复原的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.22,0:24:56.42,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你真的就那么想吗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.42,0:24:58.26,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,难道真的可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.36,0:25:05.60,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你那么吹捧的乙檀 你觉得会怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.60,0:25:11.10,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,大人 把这件事情交给了 柳乙坦是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.57,0:25:14.78,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,那要等著看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.98,0:25:19.18,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,可 你的表情怎么会那样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.18,0:25:23.22,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,难道没有找你 你觉得很难过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.32,0:25:26.15,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,听清楚了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.15,0:25:33.13,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,就算大人下命令\N也绝对不能做那件事情
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.14,0:25:47.44,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,沥青和白矾粉末
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.21,0:25:53.31,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.05,0:25:55.52,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,不知道白帆粉末吗
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.52,0:25:56.62,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,不是这个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.19,0:26:01.02,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,这个缝隙真是问题
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.39,0:26:03.22,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,难道还要有白土吗
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.96,0:26:05.79,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,我没做过这种
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.36,0:26:10.20,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,井 井儿
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.03,0:26:14.23,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,火灵呢 没来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.70,0:26:19.37,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,这些都是什么呀 怎么会在这里呀
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.47,0:26:24.14,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,是大人拿过来的 让我弄碎了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.88,0:26:28.18,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,什么 你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.28,0:26:30.75,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,-爹\N-大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.49,0:26:33.69,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,爹 你没事吗 怎么了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.42,0:26:36.62,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,哥哥帮我扶他去屋里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.83,0:26:42.50,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,井儿 这可怎么办好呀
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.60,0:26:45.80,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,居然会把那个坛子弄碎
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.17,0:26:47.63,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,那是什么坛子呀
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.74,0:26:53.51,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,大人说了什么 是叫你黏那个的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.51,0:26:57.91,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,不是啊 大人说不行 是我硬抢过来的
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.65,0:27:03.05,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,他说粘了这个会成为大逆罪人
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.05,0:27:05.62,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,粘个碗算什么 怎么会是大逆罪人呀
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.45,0:27:08.19,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,柳井
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.56,0:27:10.02,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,在 师傅
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.39,0:27:12.96,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,现在开始好好听清楚我说的话
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.06,0:27:20.30,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,打碎这个坛子\N还要黏上这个坛子的 都是我
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.67,0:27:21.77,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,明白吗
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.50,0:27:23.60,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,爹
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.60,0:27:24.34,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,柳井
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.44,0:27:26.91,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,是 师傅
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.64,0:27:28.74,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,回去睡觉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.48,0:27:30.94,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,泰道你也回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.27,0:27:57.74,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,只要确认一下就好
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.84,0:27:59.94,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.65,0:28:08.75,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,井儿
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.58,0:28:12.42,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,我能相信你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.94,0:29:39.04,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,不要跟过来
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.27,0:30:44.74,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,那个不要拿走
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.57,0:30:49.51,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,求你
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.34,0:30:53.91,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,爹 爹
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.75,0:30:57.95,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,救命呀 有山贼
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.95,0:30:59.79,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,救命呀
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.29,0:31:08.23,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,爹 爹您没事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.96,0:31:12.63,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你怎么会跟到这里来 还不快点回去
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.63,0:31:15.57,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,不要 我好害怕呀 爹
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.30,0:31:18.87,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,如果我自己遇到山贼可怎么办呀
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.48,0:31:26.95,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,爹 你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.22,0:31:38.33,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,腿好痛呀
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.10,0:31:44.20,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,呸喽
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.20,0:31:45.67,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,过了这个山就好
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.67,0:31:47.50,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,头好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.50,0:31:48.24,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,要不要我背你
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.24,0:31:49.70,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,好呀 背我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.70,0:31:54.47,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,来 背你
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.28,0:32:06.95,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,乙檀的包里里有破碎的坛子是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.95,0:32:08.06,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,包裹
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.42,0:32:12.09,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,难道说拿著那些碎片半夜逃跑了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.46,0:32:13.56,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,辛苦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.50,0:32:20.90,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,要保管破碎的坛子 最先需要做的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.90,0:32:22.00,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.00,0:32:24.57,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,找到相同的泥土
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.67,0:32:26.77,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,如此
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.77,0:32:29.34,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,他是去寻找泥土了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.81,0:32:36.68,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,柳乙檀师父他 真的负责了此事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.78,0:32:39.25,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,乙檀
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.99,0:32:45.86,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你的才能 很快便会成为你的陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.25,0:33:10.08,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,师父
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.08,0:33:13.02,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,我是乙檀 请受我一拜
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.36,0:33:22.93,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,干嘛傻站著 还不行礼
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.93,0:33:24.40,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,这是我的闺女
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.40,0:33:25.87,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,请受她一拜
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.47,0:33:34.31,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,我叫作井儿
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.26,0:33:50.46,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,磨蹭什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.46,0:33:51.92,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,赶紧给我拿出来
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.92,0:33:53.76,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,啊 是 师父
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.19,0:34:22.02,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,支离破碎了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.12,0:34:26.06,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,这么宝贝的东西怎么落得这幅田地
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.06,0:34:27.89,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,只要帮忙找到泥土 师父
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.89,0:34:30.46,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,就你这个犯了谋反罪的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.46,0:34:34.13,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,我会悄然回去 不会给师父添乱的
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.60,0:34:37.07,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,还有
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.07,0:34:39.27,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,这个孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.27,0:34:41.84,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,还请师父暂时替我照顾著
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.84,0:34:43.31,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,爹
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.31,0:34:45.51,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,若是我遭遇不测
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.51,0:34:48.45,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,井儿就托付给你了 师父
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.82,0:34:50.28,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.28,0:34:51.75,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,这不是我打碎的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.75,0:34:55.42,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,可是爹您为什么会遭遇不测呢
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.79,0:34:58.73,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,爹 求您了 不要这样
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.09,0:35:00.56,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,我来
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.56,0:35:02.40,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,我可以做得很好
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.40,0:35:06.43,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,我一定会黏的好好的 任谁都看不出来
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.43,0:35:08.64,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,那不就行了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.10,0:35:12.31,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你说你叫井儿吗
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.41,0:35:15.61,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你做过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.99,0:35:32.49,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,做成太祖大王坛子的泥土\N是金刚山的冻土
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.06,0:35:37.63,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,这些都是装泥土的坛子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.63,0:35:39.47,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你给找出来
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.83,0:35:42.04,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,在这么多泥土中吗
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.04,0:35:44.60,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,怎么 你打算放弃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.60,0:35:46.44,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,不 不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.44,0:35:48.28,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,我能找到
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.78,0:35:55.98,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,要是找到了 就给我拿来
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.72,0:35:58.19,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.56,0:36:11.40,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,上哪儿去了
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.87,0:36:14.70,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,哦 这里
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.70,0:36:15.44,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,在这儿嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.44,0:36:16.54,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.00,0:36:22.78,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,这不是井儿的四柱八字嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.14,0:36:24.98,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,您怎么还有这个呢
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.98,0:36:26.45,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,我瞧瞧
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.45,0:36:30.12,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,就算你再怎么想阻止也没用
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.12,0:36:31.59,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你瞧瞧
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.59,0:36:34.52,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,这家伙的八字这么明摆著写著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.52,0:36:36.72,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,这都是那孩子的命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.72,0:36:37.82,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你的业报
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.82,0:36:39.29,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.66,0:36:42.96,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,您觉得井儿真的能找到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.96,0:36:44.06,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.06,0:36:45.17,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,当然找不回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.17,0:36:47.37,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,没有的泥土上哪儿找去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.37,0:36:51.04,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,那您还让她去找您都不信的\N金刚山冻土吗
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.04,0:36:55.44,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你这当爹的人\N怎么就这么不懂自个儿闺女的事情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.44,0:37:00.58,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,脑门上明摆著写著 顽固不化嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.58,0:37:04.25,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,这孩子可不是让她止步就能止步的
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.25,0:37:07.55,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,得让她自己会放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.40,0:37:21.50,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,还在找吗
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.17,0:37:28.48,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,换个短命的 早就归西了
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.48,0:37:31.41,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,就算我再怎么找都没有相同的泥土啊
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.41,0:37:33.25,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,那若是如此你就如实相告便好
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.25,0:37:34.72,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,瞎磨蹭什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.72,0:37:37.65,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,若是没有相同的泥土就要做出来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.39,0:37:42.06,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,我现在正在将各种泥土混合著做出来
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.06,0:37:42.79,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,稍等片刻
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.79,0:37:44.99,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,请您稍等片刻
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.66,0:37:50.50,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,井 井 井儿
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.80,0:37:55.27,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,没有的话
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.27,0:37:57.47,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,做出来就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.18,0:38:05.91,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,乙檀啊
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.91,0:38:07.01,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.01,0:38:08.85,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,这孩子放在这儿
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.85,0:38:10.68,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你先走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.59,0:38:22.80,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,快请进
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.10,0:38:26.83,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,井儿呢
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.83,0:38:28.30,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,没见到她吗
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.30,0:38:30.14,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,男子汉大丈夫不想点大事儿
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.14,0:38:32.34,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,就只知道井儿井儿的
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.44,0:38:34.91,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,给我来一坛子米酒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.91,0:38:36.38,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,去拿米酒来
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.41,0:38:41.88,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,乙檀
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.88,0:38:44.08,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你也帮帮忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.82,0:38:45.55,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.55,0:38:47.39,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,我们泰道这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.39,0:38:50.32,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,让他当个捕卒也好 还劳烦你帮帮忙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.69,0:38:52.53,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你这家伙说的什么话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.53,0:38:56.20,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,哎哟 听说你们家\N连光海君大人都会进出的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.23,0:39:01.70,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,大人
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.70,0:39:03.90,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,看来得去找大人一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.21,0:39:08.68,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,我也去
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.51,0:39:12.71,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,我是来见光海君大人的
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.08,0:39:14.55,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,还不给我退下
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.55,0:39:17.48,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,我说 只要帮忙传句话就好
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.48,0:39:18.95,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,为什么不通融一下
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.95,0:39:20.42,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,这不是泰道嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.42,0:39:21.89,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你怎么来这儿了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.89,0:39:23.36,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,武官大人
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.84,0:39:36.94,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,大人
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.30,0:39:40.24,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,太祖大王的坛子不见了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.81,0:39:46.11,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,哦 那个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.58,0:39:51.25,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,暂时放在了我经常进出的熟人那里
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.62,0:39:54.55,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,很快就会放回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.96,0:40:00.43,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,大人
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.79,0:40:03.73,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,虽然不知大人作何想法
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.73,0:40:07.03,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,小人觉得大人很特别
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.77,0:40:11.07,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,所以大人若然觉得小人能有所帮助
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.07,0:40:14.37,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,就请放心告诉小人
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.37,0:40:16.21,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,不管是如何危险之事
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.21,0:40:18.78,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,小人都会为了大人去做
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.78,0:40:20.61,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你能如此说
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.61,0:40:22.08,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,我很感激
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.79,0:40:31.26,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,大人
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.73,0:40:36.03,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,您是信不过小人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.60,0:40:38.97,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,大人
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.64,0:40:45.94,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,有一位名叫柳乙檀的人求见
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.94,0:40:46.31,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,您打算怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.31,0:40:47.04,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,您打算怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.04,0:40:48.51,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,乙檀吗
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.24,0:40:51.45,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,带他 带他来此处
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.45,0:40:53.28,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,是 大人
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.38,0:40:57.32,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,今天能否请你先回避一下
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.32,0:40:59.52,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,我有要事和乙檀商量
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.35,0:41:02.82,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,是 大人
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.71,0:41:21.17,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,请进
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.17,0:41:22.28,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.48,0:41:26.68,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你小子就在这里等著
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.41,0:41:28.52,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.86,0:41:38.79,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,听说那野猪就是你小子抓到的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.79,0:41:40.99,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,啊 是 那个
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.99,0:41:42.46,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,等人的这会功夫
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.46,0:41:44.66,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,就来看看你小子的射箭水平吧
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.03,0:41:45.77,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.76,0:42:16.23,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,蒙上他的眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.92,0:42:43.39,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,大人
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.86,0:42:50.00,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,小人存了逆心 打碎了太祖大王的坛子
Dialogue: 0,0:42:50.00,0:42:53.30,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,所以 特来呈秉
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.30,0:42:54.77,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你现在
Dialogue: 0,0:42:55.14,0:42:56.97,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,说的是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.97,0:43:01.38,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,小人的闺女连累到大人之事死不足惜
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.38,0:43:02.84,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:43:03.94,0:43:07.61,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,她还是个不知天高地厚的孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:43:08.35,0:43:09.82,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,还请您
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.82,0:43:12.75,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,饶她一命
Dialogue: 0,0:43:13.12,0:43:14.22,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你起来
Dialogue: 0,0:43:14.22,0:43:14.96,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,大人
Dialogue: 0,0:43:14.96,0:43:19.36,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你起来 要求情的人反而是我
Dialogue: 0,0:43:20.83,0:43:22.30,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,那个坛子
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.03,0:43:24.87,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,一开始就是打碎的
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.87,0:43:25.97,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.97,0:43:30.74,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,我听说井儿对打碎的器皿\N有独到的见解
Dialogue: 0,0:43:30.74,0:43:32.21,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,心存侥幸就...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:32.57,0:43:34.41,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,若是你能帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:43:34.41,0:43:36.98,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,说不定能够成功\N出於这样的希望我就...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:36.98,0:43:40.28,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,我现在就会告诉殿下事实的真相
Dialogue: 0,0:43:40.28,0:43:42.48,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,让所有的事情回到原点
Dialogue: 0,0:43:42.48,0:43:43.58,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.58,0:43:45.42,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,不用了 大人
Dialogue: 0,0:43:46.52,0:43:48.36,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,若然如此
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.72,0:43:52.39,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,大人定会处於困境 这不用想便知
Dialogue: 0,0:43:53.13,0:43:55.33,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,大人是小人的救命恩人
Dialogue: 0,0:43:55.33,0:43:57.53,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,小人办不到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:43:57.90,0:44:01.57,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,救命恩人 你是说我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:44:02.30,0:44:03.77,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:44:04.50,0:44:06.71,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,多亏了您的出生
Dialogue: 0,0:44:06.71,0:44:10.74,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,小人才得以免去处刑 重新生活
Dialogue: 0,0:44:11.48,0:44:14.05,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,可以称之为救命恩人了
Dialogue: 0,0:44:15.88,0:44:20.65,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,井儿 您就相信她一回吧
Dialogue: 0,0:44:22.86,0:44:26.89,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,不过 若事情有变
Dialogue: 0,0:44:28.36,0:44:30.93,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,所有责任就请推卸到小人身上
Dialogue: 0,0:44:31.67,0:44:38.27,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,就请保护... 井儿那孩子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:44:43.78,0:44:45.25,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,此人如今...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:45.98,0:44:48.92,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,竟然都明目张胆的出入王宫吗
Dialogue: 0,0:44:48.92,0:44:51.85,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,说两位之间有要紧事相谈
Dialogue: 0,0:44:52.22,0:44:53.69,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,如被赶走搬出了门
Dialogue: 0,0:44:53.69,0:44:55.52,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,还会是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:44:55.89,0:44:59.93,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,把碗复原 救大人与危难之中
Dialogue: 0,0:44:59.93,0:45:03.96,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,然后要这郎厅之位 这不明摆著吗
Dialogue: 0,0:45:04.33,0:45:05.80,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:45:06.17,0:45:08.00,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,柳乙檀前辈总不会...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:08.00,0:45:10.20,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你到底是单纯还是缺根筋
Dialogue: 0,0:45:11.30,0:45:16.81,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,乙檀为何要拼上性命 帮助光海君大人
Dialogue: 0,0:45:17.54,0:45:21.95,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,承担著大逆罪人的风险\N非要复原的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:45:23.05,0:45:24.89,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,还能是什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:45:27.45,0:45:30.39,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你这身手 只在后山狩猎真是太委屈了
Dialogue: 0,0:45:30.39,0:45:33.33,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,有你这使弓箭的身手\N不管内禁卫还是兼司仆
Dialogue: 0,0:45:33.33,0:45:35.90,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,想进哪个都可以 如何
Dialogue: 0,0:45:35.90,0:45:38.47,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,您过奖了 我还有许多不足
Dialogue: 0,0:45:38.83,0:45:41.77,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,都说了 我这个兼司朴长保证了
Dialogue: 0,0:45:43.24,0:45:45.44,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,不仅是弓箭 刀法也非常了得
Dialogue: 0,0:45:46.91,0:45:48.38,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,这点我能保证
Dialogue: 0,0:45:51.68,0:45:54.98,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,等碗做完了 就带到铜器店街道
Dialogue: 0,0:45:55.72,0:45:57.18,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,四天后的未时
Dialogue: 0,0:46:10.40,0:46:11.87,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,杯子漏了
Dialogue: 0,0:46:11.87,0:46:13.33,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,漏了才对
Dialogue: 0,0:46:14.43,0:46:15.54,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:46:16.27,0:46:18.84,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,这是故意摔碎并黏起来的
Dialogue: 0,0:46:19.57,0:46:22.14,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,我还真没发现
Dialogue: 0,0:46:22.14,0:46:24.71,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,我用了鸽子白
Dialogue: 0,0:46:25.45,0:46:28.01,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,您是说鸡蛋白吗
Dialogue: 0,0:46:29.85,0:46:32.79,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,把鸡子白与黏著剂搅拌在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:46:33.15,0:46:35.72,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,就能让人察觉不到这是黏上的
Dialogue: 0,0:46:37.19,0:46:39.39,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,可一倒热水进去
Dialogue: 0,0:46:39.76,0:46:43.06,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,就会像这样鸡子白融化掉从而漏水
Dialogue: 0,0:46:44.16,0:46:46.00,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,然后就可以看到裂痕了
Dialogue: 0,0:46:46.00,0:46:48.20,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,那么您认为柳乙檀此人...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:48.94,0:46:51.51,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,也会用鸡子白吗
Dialogue: 0,0:46:51.51,0:46:52.97,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,此人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:46:54.44,0:46:59.21,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,比起称呼为前辈 要好听多了 毓道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:47:18.30,0:47:21.60,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,来 制作泥巴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:47:21.97,0:47:22.70,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:47:22.70,0:47:24.54,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,不得有黏著剂吗
Dialogue: 0,0:47:24.54,0:47:26.01,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,这是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:47:26.01,0:47:27.84,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,接著 尝尝看
Dialogue: 0,0:47:33.71,0:47:37.02,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,这是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:48:36.11,0:48:39.05,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,爹 我弄好了
Dialogue: 0,0:49:05.84,0:49:08.78,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,小丫头 费心了
Dialogue: 0,0:49:09.88,0:49:11.34,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,小小年纪
Dialogue: 0,0:50:51.91,0:50:53.01,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,师父
Dialogue: 0,0:50:53.75,0:50:57.05,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,昨夜太暗 坛子看起来比较奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:50:57.78,0:50:59.99,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,可这起来一看 完全看不出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:51:02.19,0:51:04.76,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,当然 理应如此
Dialogue: 0,0:51:05.86,0:51:07.69,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,也不看看是谁的手艺
Dialogue: 0,0:51:33.75,0:51:37.06,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你能把他们引开吗
Dialogue: 0,0:51:57.24,0:51:57.98,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,大人
Dialogue: 0,0:51:57.98,0:51:59.08,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,先跑了再说
Dialogue: 0,0:52:03.85,0:52:05.32,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,臭小子
Dialogue: 0,0:52:17.06,0:52:18.17,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:52:21.47,0:52:23.30,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,哎呦 不好意思啊 不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:52:23.30,0:52:24.77,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,臭...臭小子
Dialogue: 0,0:52:26.61,0:52:29.18,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,抓住他 抓住他
Dialogue: 0,0:52:31.75,0:52:32.85,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:52:33.58,0:52:34.68,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,给我站住
Dialogue: 0,0:52:42.39,0:52:45.33,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,来人啊 抓住他
Dialogue: 0,0:52:45.33,0:52:47.53,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,-抓住他\N-快抓住他
Dialogue: 0,0:52:47.53,0:52:50.10,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,抓住他 抓住他
Dialogue: 0,0:52:51.93,0:52:53.77,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,是罪人 是罪人
Dialogue: 0,0:53:01.48,0:53:02.58,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,火灵
Dialogue: 0,0:53:06.25,0:53:07.35,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,看来是这边
Dialogue: 0,0:53:10.28,0:53:11.02,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,开门
Dialogue: 0,0:53:12.49,0:53:13.59,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,快开门
Dialogue: 0,0:53:14.69,0:53:15.79,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,开门
Dialogue: 0,0:53:16.89,0:53:17.99,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,快开门
Dialogue: 0,0:53:34.88,0:53:36.34,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,是谁呀 砸碎这个的人
Dialogue: 0,0:53:37.44,0:53:40.38,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,这可是明国使臣带来的珍贵瓷器
Dialogue: 0,0:53:40.75,0:53:43.32,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,我要联系使臣馆 请两位稍后
Dialogue: 0,0:53:43.32,0:53:45.52,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,谁都不许走
Dialogue: 0,0:53:45.89,0:53:47.35,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,看来不在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:53:47.72,0:53:48.82,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,我们走
Dialogue: 0,0:54:09.38,0:54:12.68,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,等一下 他们还在外面
Dialogue: 0,0:54:13.78,0:54:14.51,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,再等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:54:15.98,0:54:17.82,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,再等等 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:54:44.61,0:54:45.71,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,这边
Dialogue: 0,0:55:00.39,0:55:03.70,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,那个 复原了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:55:03.70,0:55:05.53,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,啊是
Dialogue: 0,0:55:14.34,0:55:15.44,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,辛苦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:55:23.15,0:55:28.29,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你这么辛苦 想要什么 我给你买
Dialogue: 0,0:55:30.86,0:55:31.96,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,不 不走吗
Dialogue: 0,0:55:34.16,0:55:36.36,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,走吧 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:55:45.54,0:55:47.01,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,来随便挑
Dialogue: 0,0:55:53.98,0:55:55.82,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,给泰道买也可以
Dialogue: 0,0:55:56.55,0:55:59.49,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你哥也为了帮你吃了不少苦
Dialogue: 0,0:56:00.59,0:56:01.69,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:56:01.69,0:56:04.99,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,哥哥他什么忙也没有帮
Dialogue: 0,0:56:06.83,0:56:10.13,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,我爹也没有帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:56:11.60,0:56:15.64,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,只有我 跟此事有关的只有我一个
Dialogue: 0,0:56:17.84,0:56:22.61,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,这样我该做的也做完了
Dialogue: 0,0:56:26.65,0:56:30.68,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,以后大人跟我不再相见
Dialogue: 0,0:56:32.52,0:56:35.82,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,爹跟我才能平安
Dialogue: 0,0:56:38.76,0:56:41.70,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,请您多多保重
Dialogue: 0,0:56:45.00,0:56:49.77,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,请您照顾好自己
Dialogue: 0,0:57:27.57,0:57:29.78,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你怎么会在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:57:31.61,0:57:34.18,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,都说了我不会再回师父那里
Dialogue: 0,0:57:35.28,0:57:36.75,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,那井儿怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:57:36.75,0:57:39.32,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,井儿她很想你
Dialogue: 0,0:57:44.46,0:57:47.39,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,很想我 有多想
Dialogue: 0,0:57:51.06,0:57:55.47,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,因为太想我 晚上睡不著吗
Dialogue: 0,0:57:56.94,0:57:59.14,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,看著月亮哭了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:58:02.08,0:58:03.91,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,井儿就在附近
Dialogue: 0,0:58:04.64,0:58:05.75,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,我带她来
Dialogue: 0,0:58:05.75,0:58:07.95,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你还是如此执著 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:58:09.78,0:58:14.55,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,再这样下去 我怕我会恨井儿
Dialogue: 0,0:58:16.76,0:58:20.06,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,外面安静了 慢走不送
Dialogue: 0,0:58:31.07,0:58:35.11,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,这真的是你 井儿你做的
Dialogue: 0,0:58:55.30,0:58:56.40,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,大人
Dialogue: 0,0:58:57.86,0:59:01.17,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,夜深了 大人为何来此
Dialogue: 0,0:59:01.17,0:59:03.37,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,明天就是宗庙祭
Dialogue: 0,0:59:03.37,0:59:05.57,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,我来做最后的检查
Dialogue: 0,0:59:05.57,0:59:08.51,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,臣亦如此
Dialogue: 0,0:59:08.51,0:59:09.98,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,那就慢慢检查吧
Dialogue: 0,0:59:10.34,0:59:12.18,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,是 大人
Dialogue: 0,0:59:23.56,0:59:25.03,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,怎会如此
Dialogue: 0,0:59:26.13,0:59:28.33,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,简直完美无缺
Dialogue: 0,0:59:54.76,0:59:56.59,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,别做了 绝对不成
Dialogue: 0,0:59:59.89,1:00:00.99,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,您是说
Dialogue: 0,1:00:01.73,1:00:04.30,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,我去确认过
Dialogue: 0,1:00:04.30,1:00:06.87,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,简直一模一样
Dialogue: 0,1:00:08.34,1:00:14.57,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,大人 殿下发问大人只要沈默就好
Dialogue: 0,1:00:14.57,1:00:16.78,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,都说了别做了
Dialogue: 0,1:00:16.78,1:00:20.08,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,乙檀那家伙 简直就是神之手 神之手
Dialogue: 0,1:00:20.45,1:00:24.12,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,大人 就算他再怎么技艺卓群
Dialogue: 0,1:00:24.12,1:00:27.42,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,打破坛子是事实
Dialogue: 0,1:00:27.42,1:00:30.72,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,臣有办法证明
Dialogue: 0,1:00:36.60,1:00:37.70,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,大人
Dialogue: 0,1:00:41.37,1:00:43.57,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你还有脸来见我
Dialogue: 0,1:00:45.77,1:00:49.44,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,叫你打听祭阳所发生何事\N你要拖到几时
Dialogue: 0,1:00:50.54,1:00:52.75,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,我定会在殿下面前参上一本
Dialogue: 0,1:00:52.75,1:00:55.68,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,叫殿下把你分院郎厅革职查办
Dialogue: 0,1:00:55.68,1:00:57.88,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,宗庙祭结束后
Dialogue: 0,1:00:59.35,1:01:03.76,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,大人如此对我 定会后悔
Dialogue: 0,1:01:06.33,1:01:12.57,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,请您看清楚光海君大人和乙檀的下场
Dialogue: 0,1:01:17.34,1:01:19.54,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,再来练习一次祭祀礼
Dialogue: 0,1:01:22.84,1:01:25.78,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,先把太祖大王的坛子放上去
Dialogue: 0,1:01:25.78,1:01:27.61,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,是 大人
Dialogue: 0,1:01:29.82,1:01:32.39,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,主上殿下驾到
Dialogue: 0,1:01:45.60,1:01:49.64,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,祭祀前\N寡人亲自过来看看是否一切准备妥当
Dialogue: 0,1:01:52.57,1:01:57.34,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,大胆 这么珍贵的东西\N你竟敢赤手拿著
Dialogue: 0,1:02:18.27,1:02:19.37,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,大胆
Dialogue: 0,1:02:19.37,1:02:22.67,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,殿下 请殿下息怒
Dialogue: 0,1:02:22.67,1:02:28.18,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,此太祖大王的坛子摔碎了
Dialogue: 0,1:02:28.18,1:02:29.28,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,摔碎
Dialogue: 0,1:02:57.54,1:02:59.01,Next2,,0,0,0,,*下集预告*
Dialogue: 0,1:03:00.11,1:03:01.94,Next2,,0,0,0,,把他带下去
Dialogue: 0,1:03:01.94,1:03:03.78,Next2,,0,0,0,,就上经一次 请网开一面
Dialogue: 0,1:03:03.78,1:03:07.45,Next2,,0,0,0,,这是证明坛子曾经摔碎过的唯一办法
Dialogue: 0,1:03:07.45,1:03:09.28,Next2,,0,0,0,,此次铲除对象是光海君
Dialogue: 0,1:03:09.28,1:03:12.59,Next2,,0,0,0,,让无辜之人蒙受不白之冤\N难道这就是殿下的王道
Dialogue: 0,1:03:12.59,1:03:14.42,Next2,,0,0,0,,给我住嘴
Dialogue: 0,1:03:14.42,1:03:15.16,Next2,,0,0,0,,你们干什么
Dialogue: 0,1:03:15.16,1:03:16.62,Next2,,0,0,0,,快回家去 快
Dialogue: 0,1:03:16.62,1:03:19.93,Next2,,0,0,0,,把我爹放了 抓我
Dialogue: 0,1:03:19.93,1:03:21.03,Next2,,0,0,0,,你去做个碗来
Dialogue: 0,1:03:21.03,1:03:22.50,Next2,,0,0,0,,我不会做碗
Dialogue: 0,1:03:22.50,1:03:25.07,Next2,,0,0,0,,定要重罚
Dialogue: 0,1:03:25.07,1:03:27.27,Next2,,0,0,0,,她跟我一样 一出生就没了娘
Dialogue: 0,1:03:27.27,1:03:28.74,Next2,,0,0,0,,我娘生下我后就...
Dialogue: 0,1:03:28.74,1:03:30.57,Next2,,0,0,0,,本就该斩草除根
Dialogue: 0,1:03:30.57,1:03:32.41,Next2,,0,0,0,,寡人会再思量
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.55,0:00:58.75,comment2,,0,0,0,,第3回
